		<description></description>
		<content:encoded>
				<![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>These are 3 bits of a musical which I wrote with my friend James Colclough, a great theatre producer and singing teacher. (One of his students currently starring in Mama Mia in London’s West End.) I wrote the songs and most of the plot  and Jim said “No, you can’t do that, or that -but how about this?” And he was bleeding’ right Every Time! Great working with you Jim!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

